// GET THE LOGOUT
router.get("/logout", function (req, res, next) {
    if (req.session) {
        req.session.destroy(function (err) {
            if (err) {
                return next(err);
            }
            else {
                return res.status(200).redirect("/");
            }
        });
    }
});
